 很快就不得不降低门票费用</a>，因为门票价格也因高峰定价而被抬高。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 于格拉斯顿伯里和纳内沃斯 (Glastonbury &amp; Knebworth) 的石玫瑰 (The Stone Roses) 演出第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j27A15yBBE8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Oasis 向歌迷承诺，2025 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-plans-underway-for-2025-shows-outside-of-europe-3787647">在欧洲以外地区的演出计划“正在进行中”</a> ，而现在，Oasis 似乎正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-seem-to-be-hinting-at-us-dates-in-new-billboard-poster-3789935">用全美各地的广告牌来调侃美国的演出日期</a>。乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">明确表示，他们明年不会在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上担任主角，也不会出现在任何音乐节上</a>。</p><p>除了 Gallaghers 之外<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">，重组后的乐队阵容还有</a>很多谜团和猜测，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">Bonehead</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gem-archer-is-looking-very-likely-to-join-oasis-line-up-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3789719">Gem Archer 都将担任吉他手</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alan-white-teases-joining-oasis-reunion-line-up-3789548">Alan White 开玩笑说他将回到鼓手位置</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">绿洲乐队以额外的温布利演出回应重聚巡演门票争议——通过邀请投票</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
